ilit\u00e9 de certaines personnes.\nSi vous le souhaitez, vous pouvez retirer votre casque \u00e0 tout moment.", "short_description": "Vid\u00e9os 360\u00b0 interactive pour sensibiliser au harc\u00e8lement.\n\nLe film que vous allez voir est une fiction pouvant heurter la sensibilit\u00e9 de certaines personnes.\nSi vous le souhaitez, vous pouvez retirer votre casque \u00e0 tout moment."}]}, "developer_name": "iCAP - Universit\u00e9 Lyon 1", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://virtuallab.univ-lyon1.fr/privacy-policy-for-heureusement-que-tu-etais-la/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "iCAP - Universit\u00e9 Lyon 1", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://virtuallab.univ-lyon1.fr/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1283811691952063"}, {"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["fr"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7534010613355910"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031379_7655162934543572_3030116165418173802_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yzotNncT-4UQ7kNvgENwBTo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AljZ8bO4TUvalfb1n6kF7oD&oh=00_AYDXSta9Z1JiGY3iUAOJNC0rRSWLDTihkRRnjUxAIMty9Q&oe=66F69260"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Heureusement que tu \u00e9tais l\u00e0 !", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_